::Feline::
She giggled as he tickled her. She reached out and tickled him back. 
She laughs.



KitKat::
She smiled and kissed Drillbit.  She then winced at her ribs and took 
few steps away from the CR chamber.  She looked at him, "Please, tell 
me what has happened? I don't remember anything after falling from 
the ship. Where are we?  What has happened to the others? What's 
happening now with the group? Did everyone get out ok?"

Her mind went reeling around, wanting to know that all her team mates 
where ok and that she still had a group to function with.
